Package org.spdx.library.conversion

Class Spdx2to3Converter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spdx.library.conversion.Spdx2to3Converter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISpdxConverter
    public class Spdx2to3Converter
extends Object
implements ISpdxConverter
    Author:
    Gary O'Neall

    Converts SPDX spec version 2.X objects to SPDX spec version 3.X and stores the result in the toModelStore
